# 🚀 Universal Git Ignore for Backend & Frontend
# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

### 🟢 Frontend (React) ###
/frontend/node_modules/
/frontend/.pnp
/frontend/.pnp.js
/frontend/.next/
/frontend/.cache/
/frontend/build/
/frontend/dist/
/frontend/.env.local
/frontend/.DS_Store

### 🟢 Backend (Python) ###
/backend/__pycache__/
/backend/*.pyc
/backend/.venv/
/backend/.pytest_cache/
/backend/chatbot-env/
/backend/firebase_key.json  # Firebase credentials
chatbot-env/  # Virtual environment (outside backend too)

/backend/.DS_Store  # macOS system files

### 🟢 Firebase & Env Variables ###
/firebase_key.json  # Ensure it's ignored globally
/.env  # Root environment files
/backend/.env  # Backend-specific env
/frontend/.env  # Frontend-specific env

### 🟢 Logs & Debug ###
/npm-debug.log*
/yarn-debug.log*
/yarn-error.log*
/coverage
/logs/
/*.log
/backend/*.log
/frontend/*.log

### 🟢 OS-Specific Files ###
.DS_Store  # macOS junk
Thumbs.db  # Windows junk
